{"tid":1944044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍驅逐艦周三駛經台海做演練","createTime":"2020-03-26T06:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T22:34:51.000Z","uid":95138,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe535f53697b9dbd3a7ba29b063b85e3cd7afa8","tid":1944044,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"美軍驅逐艦昨日駛經台海。<br />\n<br />\n美國太平洋艦隊發放圖片，指屬第七艦隊的導彈驅逐艦「麥克坎貝爾」號，周三駛經台海做各項演練，其間有用作反潛任務的海鷹直升機升空，亦有美軍操作艦上設備，及在艦橋監視海面。台灣的國防部指，該艘美軍驅逐艦昨日<span style=\"color: red;\">從台灣西南海域，由南向北、駛經台灣海峽。</span>當局全程掌握周邊海空域動態，沒有異樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/21460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F21460&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=35c9e1e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F21460&h=a0ab012c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/21460</a>"},{"pid":"3aed68d4f236206fd85367870559ea5619dc1564","tid":1944044,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"支那繼續話假"},{"pid":"c54da7cedf9ce352decd68123fd5396fd209ce34","tid":1944044,"uid":95138,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rndy6Mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frndy6Mx.jpg&h=3114b2d5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/62418562969/posts/10158017078892970/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F62418562969%2Fposts%2F10158017078892970%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWRwKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=5d245231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/62418562969/posts/10158017078892970/</a>"},{"pid":"46cbc14145de7c6609be49911ca0b5f7291eb89d","tid":1944044,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,